{"lemma":"أَعْمَى","slug":"أَعْمَى","root":"ع.م.#","root_slug":"ع-م-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-م-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"أَعْمَى","root":"عمي","pos":"N","occurrence_count":21},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":0},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n30634"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%92%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%89"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n30634","headword_ar":"اَعْمَى","root":"EmY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamK","text_ar":"عَمٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K [but see what follows])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Blind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of both eyes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K, * TA:) fem. of the former"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamoyaA='u","text_ar":"عَمْيَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb, K, TA:) and pl. [masc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EumoYN","text_ar":"عُمْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, TA, but not in the CK) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EumoyaAnN","text_ar":"عُمْيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K, TA, but not in the CK) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EumaApN","text_ar":"عُمَاةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as though this last were pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmK","text_ar":"عَامٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA, but not in the CK;) and the dual of its fem. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamoyaAwaAni","text_ar":"عَمْيَاوَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and its pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamoyaAwaAtN","text_ar":"عَمْيَاوَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) the fem. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamK","text_ar":"عَمٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamiyapN","text_ar":"عَمِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, TA, [in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamiy~apN","text_ar":"عَمِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is a mistranscription, for it is]) of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEilapN","text_ar":"فَعِلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariHapN","text_ar":"فَرِحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamoyapN","text_ar":"عَمْيَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA, but not in the CK,) which is [a contraction] like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faxo*N","text_ar":"فَخْذٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faxi*N","text_ar":"فَخِذٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and the pl. masc. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamuwna","text_ar":"عَمُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, TA.) ―         -b2-  And [hence,] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Blind in respect of the mind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) [but more commonly] one says, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa EamK","text_ar":"هُوَ عَمٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is erring,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one who errs;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEomaY Alqalobi","text_ar":"اَعْمَى القَلْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning the same, or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blind in respect of the mind"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Msb:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alqalobi","text_ar":"القَلْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN EamiY","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ عَمِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An ignorant man"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a man blind in respect of the mind"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AimoraA^apN EamiyapN Eani AlS~awaAbi","text_ar":"اِمْرَاَةٌ عَمِيَةٌ عَنِ الصَّوَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a woman ignorant of,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blind to, that which is right"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamiyapu Alqalobi","text_ar":"عَمِيَةُ القَلْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamiY Alqalobi","text_ar":"عَمِى القَلْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as applied to a man]. (S.) In the saying in the Kur [xvii. 74],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wamano","text_ar":"وَمَنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna fiY h`*ihi fahuwa fiY A@loA=xirapi A^aEomaY","text_ar":"كَانَ فِى هٰذِهِ فَهُوَ فِى ا@لْا=خِرَةِ اَعْمَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to Er-Rághib, the former ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEmY","text_ar":"اعمى"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is a part. n. and the second is like it; (TA;) and the meaning is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And whoso is in this"},{"kind":"text","text":"state of existence"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blind in respect of the mind, not seeing his right course, he will be in the other blind with respect to the way of safety:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd:) or, as some say, the second is what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afoEalu tafoDiylK","text_ar":"اَفْعَلُ تَفْضِيلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the complement of which is expressed by means of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino","text_ar":"مِنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"more blind"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,] and therefore AA and Yaakoob did not pronounce it with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_imaAlap","text_ar":"الاـِمَالَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", as not being like the first, (Bd, TA, *) which is subject to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAmAlp","text_ar":"الامالة"},{"kind":"text","text":"because its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"] becomes [really]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the dual: but Hamzeh and Ks and Aboo-Bekr pronounced both with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAmAlp","text_ar":"الامالة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Bd.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^aEomayaAni","text_ar":"الاَعْمَيَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The torrent and the fire of a burning house"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) because of the perplexity that befalls him whom they befall; or because, when they occur, they spare not a place, nor avoid anything; like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEomaY","text_ar":"اَعْمَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or blind], who knows not where he is travelling, so that he goes whither his leg conveys him: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the torrent and the night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the torrent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the tumultuous torrent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the camel excited by lust."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^amoru","text_ar":"الاَمْرُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^aEomaY","text_ar":"الاَعْمَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The case"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as that"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of partisanship"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEaSabiy~ap","text_ar":"العَصَبِيَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whereof the manner of proceeding is not distinguishable."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN EamoyaA='u","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ عَمْيَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmiyapN","text_ar":"عَامِيَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"makaAnN A^aEomaY","text_ar":"مَكَانٌ اَعْمَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A land,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place, in which one will not,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cannot, be directed to his right course."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b6-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sak~apa EumaY~K","text_ar":"صَكَّةَ عُمَىٍّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": ―         -b7-  and see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamiy~apN","text_ar":"عَمِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA","Bd"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}